25
00:05:03,170 --> 00:05:04,120
C'est lui !

26
00:05:04,320 --> 00:05:05,260
Stop !

27
00:05:14,180 --> 00:05:15,730
Il est là !

28
00:05:16,850 --> 00:05:18,150
Chopez le.

29
00:05:36,750 --> 00:05:38,110
Vous, à gauche !

30
00:05:38,310 --> 00:05:40,210
Attrapez le !
Tuez le s'il faut !

31
