299
00:22:03,570 --> 00:22:05,070
<i>J'aimerais tellement !</i>

300
00:22:05,570 --> 00:22:06,740
<i>Restez concentrés.</i>

301
00:22:08,740 --> 00:22:10,730
<i>Vous passez les 5.000 m.</i>

