00:26:07,730 --> 00:26:09,400
<i>Brouillage activé.</i>

385
00:26:10,860 --> 00:26:12,780
Alerte. Des megs.

386
00:26:16,360 --> 00:26:17,530
J'y crois pas...

387
00:26:28,620 --> 00:26:30,790
J'en ai jamais vu
